Day 4 Answers

## 1. What is Flow Builder?

Flow Builder is a Salesforce tool used to automate business processes without coding.

---

## 2. Types of Flows

### Screen Flow
- User input required
- Used for guided processes

### Record-Triggered Flow
- Runs automatically
- Triggered by record changes

---

## 3. Why Automation Helps

- Reduces manual effort
- Improves accuracy
- Saves time
- Increases efficiency

---

## 4. Manual vs Automated Process

### Manual
- Human handling
- Slow process
- Error-prone

### Automated
- System-driven
- Fast and accurate
- No manual work needed

---

## 5. Why Companies Automate Processes

- Handle large data efficiently
- Reduce human errors
- Improve business speed
- Standardize processes
